citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"冇咩事 唔好除<br />\n除非你抓落單 手頭上冇裝 先好用<br />\n講緊lol"},{"pid":"10bdc54d3ee3913fa8146c91ec3e70b5e060706a","tid":1245671,"uid":21095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7acd72d7ccc845ed0d116babdc041a100bae9377","tid":1245671,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"發夢見到好多頭盔掉咗出去<br />\n留返比自己友好過啦<br />\n毫無殺傷力而且都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a4feb4d88b1f10d0c7b16138ffd3a81e2174639f","tid":1245671,"uid":122752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7eaf0cca7e77b0bd1157c81aff90a3c45b478e7a","tid":1245671,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a2444c0184542c9886166f23f4c4f59dc855fa","tid":1245671,"uid":156936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:15.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n【不內哄、不分化、各自上山】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>======20/6/2019 17:00更新======</strong></span><br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港親共商店地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=17b62553\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc09c47d0ae7570ad4a148744d2e6fa50986072","tid":1245671,"uid":263181,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"發夢見到啲人掉頭盔 當堂呆左<br />\n明明已經嚴重供不應求"},{"pid":"55472641a150893ac7ec95661274133df8b259d2","tid":1245671,"uid":43516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"呢個真係推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd帽得防冇攻擊力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地盤d帽好難拎咁多出嚟"},{"pid":"6af5a19ad2c6166a9f5246c766a5bbe359dc9048","tid":1245671,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"［突發！］政總聽日唔開<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245763</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54961aa3aa991eaf6365e2615be3e411c86c1d57","tid":1245671,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77768f968e7ec68d70d99e3cd35093a5bd3e534d","tid":1245671,"uid":162137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3285dd73d6177c0a5e5f3cacac079deaa06b388d","tid":1245671,"uid":63202,"lik